### Delete a customer image
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/profiles/{{profileTypeCustomer}}/{{customerId}}/images/{{imageId}}
Accept: application/json

### List images for a lead
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/profiles/{{profileTypeLead}}/{{leadId}}/images
Accept: application/json

### Upload images for a lead
